latestPosts.caption:
If you’re one of those who loves exploring delicious food and aesthetic ambience then you must checkout this place located in khar west, just a short walk from khar station and you’re here, it is a perfect place for dinner date night or the brunch date, 🍲 @thecorrnerroom is a perfect combination of cozy and homely vibes, it offers indoor and outdoor dine-in options, whether you choose Air-conditioned seating option or the outdoor alfresco with beautiful lightings and warm vibes, it also has a bar counter which is perfect to chill and relax, and the food was amazing with the perfect ambience, so do check-out and explore this beautiful spot ❤️

Foods we tried: 
Sicillian prawns
Jerk chicken 
Smoked chicken pizza
Piccata with mushroom sauce 

Drinks: 
Beach day cranberry 
Peach virgin mojito

Dessert: 
Biscoff cheesecake (must try) ❤️
